===========================
Babble SMS README
===========================

+++++++++++++
Introduction
+++++++++++++
This software module is a turnkey application that allows for sending and/or
receiving of SMS through an easy-to-use website interface. It is designed with
the look-and-feel of an email account.

Underneath it relies on the SMS Gateway as a transport mechanism for SMS to and
from the network operators.

A sample of the application can be viewed on the following website:
http://babblesms.tawi.mobi
Username: 'demo'
Password: 'demo'
